  <h2>The Essentials</h2>

  <h3>Flights</h3>
  <p><strong>Out:</strong> OS332 &middot; Fri 9 Oct &middot; 09:05 &middot; London Heathrow &rarr; Vienna<br>
  <strong>Back:</strong> OS337 &middot; Mon 12 Oct &middot; 17:15 &middot; Vienna &rarr; London Heathrow</p>

  <h3>Accommodation</h3>
  <p><strong><a href="https://www.rocksure.com/properties/vienna-apartment" style="color:#c4a97d;" target="_blank">Rocksure Vienna Apartment</a></strong> &mdash; a beautifully furnished 2-bedroom, 2-bathroom apartment on the first floor of a former palace. Quiet residential street near Mariahilferstra&szlig;e (Vienna&rsquo;s main shopping street). Spacious living room, separate sitting room, modern kitchen, air conditioning. 24-hour Rocksure concierge.</p>

  <h3>Getting Around</h3>
  <p>Almost everything on this itinerary is <strong>walkable</strong>. The apartment is perfectly placed between the MuseumsQuartier, Naschmarkt, and the Innere Stadt (old town). For Sch&ouml;nbrunn, take the U4 metro (15 mins). For Grinzing (Heuriger), take Tram 38 from Schottentor (25 mins).</p>
